OL,5,GBBC Northern Ireland's main local news
OL,6,Gprogramme, BBC Newsline, launched a new
OL,7,Glook today.
OL,9,FToday's breakfast and lunchtime
OL,10,Fprogrammes were broadcast from the
OL,11,Ftemporary set in Studio 1 at
OL,12,FBroadcasting House in Belfast. The
OL,13,Ftemporary facility has been in use
OL,14,Fsince August, whilst construction and
OL,15,Ftechnical testing of the new set-up in
OL,16,FStudio B was in progress.
OL,3,CBBC Newsline launches new look
OL,22,                                   G1/3
