OL,5,FThe updated set in Studio B was
OL,6,Frevealed on air at 6.30pm. It's based
OL,7,Fon the design and technology used in
OL,8,FStudio B at New Broadcasting House in
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,FThe Belfast set-up includes a desk, a
OL,12,Fmonolith video tower and a large
OL,13,Frectangular videowall.
OL,15,FStudio B retains its green screen
OL,16,Ffacility which adjoins the main
OL,17,Fphysical set. A virtual set is used for
OL,18,Fthe sports segment within the 6.30pm
OL,19,Fweekday programme.
OL,3,CBBC Newsline launches new look
