OL,5,FThe weather presenter utilises a large
OL,6,Fsection of the main videowall for the
OL,7,Fweather forecast at the end of the
OL,8,F6.30pm programme. All other weather
OL,9,Felements (including during the 6.30pm
OL,10,Fopening headlines) are based in the
OL,11,Fsmall Studio C green screen facility.
OL,13,FIt seems that reporters/correspondents
OL,14,Fwill also make use of the main
OL,15,Fvideowall for visual journalism, to
OL,16,Fhelp convey key information to viewers.
OL,3,CBBC Newsline launches new look
